Ndị otu cricket ụmụ nwanyị Naịjịria gara Rwanda na Septemba 2019 iji kpọọ egwuregwu ise nke Women's Twenty20 International (WT20I). Ìgwè abụọ ahụ agbaala egwuregwu ise na Abuja, Naịjirịa na Jenụwarị 2019, na Naịjirịa meriri 3o2. Njem nloghachi a bụ oge Rwanda na-anabata Naịjirịa.
E mere egwuregwu ahụ na Gahanga International Cricket Stadium na Kigali. N'ụzọ megidere usoro gara aga n'etiti akụkụ abụọ ahụ, Rwanda meriri usoro ahụ site na egwuregwu 3 na 2.
